---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs ProvenExpert — Simpler reviews for service businesses | SocialProof" description="ProvenExpert is complex and expensive for most small businesses. SocialProof gives you beautiful testimonial widgets free to start, $9/mo Pro." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/provenexpert">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f0f0f0; color: #555; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: #3730a3; }
    .price-callout { display: inline-flex; gap: 2rem; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .price-callout .item { text-align: center; }
    .price-callout .item .price { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .price-callout .item .label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #777; margin-top: .2rem; }
    .price-callout .item.vouch .price { color: #4f46e5; }
    .price-callout .item.other .price { color: #dc2626; }
    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .compare-table th { padding: .75rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #888; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; }
    .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { color: #4f46e5; }
    .compare-table td { padding: .85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 0.97rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .compare-table td:first-child { color: #555; font-weight: 500; }
    .yes { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .no { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; }
    .partial { color: #d97706; font-weight: 600; }
    .winner-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .winner-card { border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; }
    .winner-card.vouch { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #86efac; }
    .winner-card.other { background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; }
    .winner-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 .75rem; }
    .winner-card ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    .winner-card li { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #444; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
    .savings-box { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .savings-box h3 { margin: 0 0 .5rem; font-size: 1rem; }
    .savings-box p { margin: 0; color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .bottom-cta { text-align: center; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3.5rem 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; }
    .bottom-cta h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .bottom-cta p { color: #c7d2fe; margin: 0 auto 2rem; max-width: 500px; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: #fff; color: #4f46e5; padding: .9rem 2.25rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .faq-item { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .faq-item h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .5rem; }
    .faq-item p { color: #555; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
    footer { border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; color: #999; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .winner-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .price-callout { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; } }
</style>
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/vs/">Compare</a>
    <a href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-nav">Try free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <span class="vs-badge">SocialProof vs ProvenExpert</span>
  <h1>A focused alternative to <span>ProvenExpert</span> for service businesses</h1>
  <p>ProvenExpert packs in surveys, review management, and certifications. SocialProof does one thing brilliantly: puts your best customer words on your website where they convert.</p>
  <div class="price-callout">
    <div class="item vouch">
      <div class="price">Free–$9</div>
      <div class="label">SocialProof / month</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item other">
      <div class="price">$49+</div>
      <div class="label">ProvenExpert / month</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="hero-cta">Start free — no credit card</a>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>Side-by-side comparison</h2>
  <table class="compare-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Feature</th>
        <th>SocialProof</th>
        <th>ProvenExpert</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Starting price</td>
        <td><span class="yes">Free forever</span></td>
        <td><span class="no">$49/mo (Basic)</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Testimonial collection</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Yes</span></td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Yes</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Embed widget on your site</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Free plan included</span></td>
        <td><span class="partial">Paid plans only</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Star rating display</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Yes</span></td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Yes</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Review/survey management</td>
        <td><span class="partial">Focused on testimonials</span></td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Full suite</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>ProvenExpert profile page</td>
        <td><span class="no">N/A</span></td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Yes</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Google review import</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Yes</span></td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Yes</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>No-code widget embed</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ 1-line script tag</span></td>
        <td><span class="partial">More complex setup</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Setup time</td>
        <td><span class="yes">Under 5 minutes</span></td>
        <td><span class="partial">Longer learning curve</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Focused on US small business</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Core focus</span></td>
        <td><span class="partial">German-origin, international</span></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Who wins for which use case?</h2>
  <div class="winner-grid">
    <div class="winner-card vouch">
      <h3>✅ SocialProof is better if you…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Need testimonials on your site — nothing more, nothing less</li>
        <li>Are a solo operator or small local business</li>
        <li>Want to be set up in under 5 minutes</li>
        <li>Don't have $49+/mo to spend on review management</li>
        <li>Want clean, modern widgets that match your brand</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="winner-card other">
      <h3>Consider ProvenExpert if you…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Want a full review platform with surveys and certifications</li>
        <li>Need a public ProvenExpert profile listing</li>
        <li>Have an enterprise team managing reputation at scale</li>
        <li>Already use German business platforms and want integration</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="savings-box">
    <h3>💰 Save $480+ per year</h3>
    <p>SocialProof Pro at $9/mo vs ProvenExpert Basic at $49/mo. That's $480 back annually — and for most small businesses, SocialProof does everything they actually need.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Simplicity wins for small businesses</h2>
  <p style="color:#555; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">ProvenExpert is a comprehensive reputation platform with surveys, certifications, team features, and a German-language heritage. For medium-sized agencies or enterprises managing dozens of review sources, it can be a fit.</p>
  <p style="color:#555; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">But if you're a local service business — a plumber, a personal trainer, a real estate agent — you don't need all that. You need your customers' words on your website, displayed beautifully, driving new bookings.</p>
  <p style="color:#555; line-height:1.7;">That's what SocialProof does. Paste one script tag. Done.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Does SocialProof work for local service businesses?</h3>
    <p>Yes — that's exactly who we're built for. Cleaners, contractors, trainers, stylists, therapists, and hundreds of other service business types are already using SocialProof to convert more website visitors into paying clients.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Can I import existing reviews from Google?</h3>
    <p>Yes. SocialProof lets you import testimonials from Google and other sources and display them in your widget — no manual copy-paste required.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Is there a free plan?</h3>
    <p>Absolutely. Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card. No time limit. Upgrade to Pro ($9/mo) for unlimited widgets and custom branding.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>How long does setup take?</h3>
    <p>Most users are live in under 5 minutes. You create your account, add a couple of testimonials, copy a script tag, and paste it into your website. Your widget appears instantly.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="bottom-cta">
    <h2>Try the simpler way to collect and display testimonials</h2>
    <p>Free forever for 1 widget. No credit card, no setup fees, no complexity.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-btn">Get started free →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2025 SocialProof · <a href="/privacy" style="color:#999">Privacy</a> · <a href="/terms" style="color:#999">Terms</a> · <a href="/vs/" style="color:#999">All comparisons</a></p>
</footer>

<div class="footer-links" style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:0.9rem;">
  <strong style="color:#374151;">Also explore:</strong>
  <a href="/for/coaches" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Coaches</a>
  <a href="/for/freelancers" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Freelancers</a>
  <a href="/for/ecommerce" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Ecommerce</a>
  <a href="/vs/senja" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Senja</a>
  <a href="/vs/testimonial" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Testimonial.to</a>
</div>
</Base>
